

# Install Fish
sudo apt install fish

# Run Fish Shell
fish

# Optional Below Here:
# Remove Greeting
set fish_greeting

- Install fish - source (3.1.2)

- get last release in https://github.com/fish-shell/fish-shell/releases

In case you get this below error:

CMake Error: The following variables are used in this project, but they are set to NOTFOUND.
Please set them or make sure they are set and tested correctly in the CMake files:
CURSES_CURSES_LIBRARY (ADVANCED)
    linked by target "fishlib" in directory /home/lucio/Downloads/fish-3.1.2

So, procede this way:

$ sudo apt install ncurses-dev
$ cd build
$ cmake ..
$ make
$ sudo make install
$ which fish


### spacefish
https://github.com/matchai/spacefish


- Install spacefish Oh My Fish!

$ curl -L https://get.oh-my.fish | fish
or, using proxy
$ curl -s -x http://proxy-ima.ima.sp.gov.br:3128 -L https://get.oh-my.fish | fish

$ omf install spacefish

- (option) Install spacefish using Fisher

$ fisher add matchai/spacefish

# Powerline fonts
https://github.com/powerline/fonts

sudo apt install fonts-powerline

# Set Fish Shell
chsh -s /usr/bin/fish

or

put at the end of .bashrc:
fish
